  "texts": [
    "We make the following main contributions.i.)",
    "We present our anomaly detector in Section 3. ii.)",
    "An extended solution is proposed in Section 4 to detect anomalies that stand out over a longer period of time. iii.)",
    "We compare our solution results with AI/ML models for anomaly detection and explainable AI (see Section 5). iv.)",
    "We discuss how explainability [14] is incorporated into our solution (see Section 6.5)."
  ]
}